   * ARexx - Nick Veitch talks you through the power of the ADDRESS command.
   * Banging the Metal - Simon Goodwin runs through the Amiga's palette system.
   * Amiga.net - Dave Cusick reckons that email is the net's killer app.

Coverdisks
